## Partie 8 — Exposition de l'application (Service NodePort)

Créez `app-service.yaml` :

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: node-app-service
  namespace: tp-app-mysql
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: node-app
  ports:
    - port: 80
      targetPort: 3000
      nodePort: 30080
```

```bash
kubectl apply -f app-service.yaml
```

Récupérez l'URL d'accès :

```bash
minikube service node-app-service -n tp-app-mysql --url
```

Testez avec curl :

```bash
curl $(minikube service node-app-service -n tp-app-mysql --url)
curl $(minikube service node-app-service -n tp-app-mysql --url)/health
```

